  "storyline": "# Storyline\n\n## Context\n\nProduct and marketing teams needed to know which app attributes actually correlate with market fit across a noisy 2.5M-record store catalog.\n\n## Workflow\n\nCategory-level data slicing → chi-square feature engineering → trend modeling → Tableau dashboards → strategy recommendations.\n\n## Technical Implementation\n\n- **Analysis:** 2.5M+ records with Pandas/NumPy and SQL, structured into category slices.\n- **Features:** chi-square testing across 10+ attributes (size, gamification, utility) to rank market-fit KPIs.\n- **Modeling:** Scikit-learn regression trend models on rating/install signals, producing reproducible category-growth benchmarks.\n- **Dashboards:** 3 Tableau views translating signals for non-technical teams.\n\n## Outcomes\n\nTurned statistical signal into 3 development-strategy recommendations aligned to product-team decision questions."
